# Progress - ExchangeOut Route Test Coverage

## Recent Work

### Uniswap V2 Bug Fix
- **File**: `contracts/protocols/dexes/uniswap/v2/UniswapV2StandardExchangeOutTarget.sol`
- **Issue**: `indexSource.pool` was not initialized before calling `_loadIndexSourceReserves` in `exchangeOut`
- **Fix**: Added early pool initialization at line 364
- **Test**: Added `UniswapV2StandardExchangeOut_PassThrough.t.sol` with 6 tests verifying preview == execution

### Balancer V3 Router Bug Fix
- **File**: `contracts/protocols/dexes/balancer/v3/routers/BalancerV3StandardExchangeRouterExactOutSwapTarget.sol`
- **Issue**: In Vault Pass-Through route with WETH unwrap, used `params.limit` instead of `estimatedAmountIn` when calling `vault.exchangeOut` with `pretransferred=true`
- **Fix**: Changed line 231 from `params.limit` to `estimatedAmountIn`
- **Test**: Added `BalancerV3StandardExchangeRouter_WethUnwrap.t.sol` with 6 tests

